templateVersions.content:
0.Summary of Finding and Opportunities
{!$Input:FindingsAndOpportunities}

1. **Customer Name, Id and Premise Address:**
{!$Flow:Get_Account_Data.Prompt}

2. **From the following product and service catalog, recommend the most important products/services that address the issues you identified in the data. In addition to the primary product, also identify and include any related services (e.g., an installation service for a physical product). Do not recommend a product if there is no clear evidence for it.**
 {!$Flow:Get_Non_commodity_Products_Services.Prompt}

4.From the summary of Finding and Opportunities provide a final response as a JSON object with the following structure. Make the field values dynamic based on your analysis. If no products/services are recommended, only include the "AnalysisSummary" field. Otherwise, include "EnergyOpportunity" and "EnergyQuote" as well.  
 
{ "AccountId": "AccountId", "AnalysisSummary": "Detailed summary of the energy analysis, covering key findings from metering data, contract evaluation, and identified risks, inefficiencies, or opportunities. This summary should provide enough detail for a case to be created even if no specific product recommendations are made.", "EnergyOpportunity": { "Name": "Define a clear name for the opportunity", "Description": "Summary of the opportunity that will help the Key account Manager understand it" }, "EnergyQuote": { "Name": "Define Clear name for the quote", "EnergyQuoteLineItems": [ { "Product2Id": "Product2Id", "Quantity": 1, "Description": "Summary of why the product/service is suggested", "ProductName": "ProductName", "PricebookEntryId": "PricebookEntryId" } ] } }
